prodNameC: 免疫特 肌紅蛋白試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1. Myoglobin Test Units (LMY1):
Each unit contain one bead coated with monoclonal murine anti-myoglobin antibody.
2. Myoglobin Reagent Wedge (LMY2):
6.5 mL alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal goat anti-myoglobin antibody in buffer, with preservative.
3. Myoglobin Adjustors (LMYL, LMYH):
Two vials (Low and High) 2.0 mL each.
4. Myoglobin Sample Diluent (LMYZ):
One vial, 25 mL.
